text: Tõnu Haljand (1 July 1945 - 28 August 1997) was an Estonian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Estonian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Estonian male biathletes Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn
